$BR
${BBOLD}Note:$EBOLD
If there is more than one answer, give them as a comma separated
list.  If there are none, enter ${BITALIC}NONE${EITALIC}.
END_TEXT

Context("Numeric");
ANS(List($x2, -$x1)->cmp);
